race.comment: KARACHI (3) hit the ground running off the tricky draw last start and was never headed (16.92) at this track in a T3 RSTW over 300m. The form out of last race has been strong. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. AWE WELL (1) was prominent throughout when winning two back then got further back last time but came home hard into third and beaten 6 lengths at Sale (24.86). Expected to feature. YEAH YOU (8) produced a moderate effort last time when fifth at Warragul over 400m behind Blue Labubu (23.59) in a Mix 6/7. Can measure up this time. SONG ABOUT SUSAN (2) can play a role coming off a short let-up.
